text: Robert Hassell (24 February 1929 - June 2004) was a British sports shooter. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:2004 deaths Category:British male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Great Britain Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from London
